title: Happy Birthday Jesus, Sorry Your Party's so Lame
description:
A few days ago the Alberta government rolled out the new restrictions for the next 4 weeks...revealing that Christmas get togethers are not allowed. So basically Christmas is cancelled...the following is a bit of a rant, but also curious how you all are doing as well

Follow me on Twitter @AndreaLynnLewis
email me at andreawiththebangs@gmail.com
